  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synopsis:</h2><br>Demons have risen from above and below. Monsters eat humans and digest them into their greatest fears. A hero awakens from afar.<br><br>Explore a massive interconnected labyrinth of grottos, castles, and groves in this 2D retro-inspired Action RPG.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867070/extras/9318c656f16ae7892aa822078e4d49f8.avif?t=1643786199\" width=630 height=132 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Massive Interconnected World<br></li><li>Tons of bosses and enemies<br></li><li>Useful Items that change player appearance<br></li><li>Tons of optional content, multiple paths to beat the game.<br></li><li>Fighter, Archer, Magician playstyles<br></li><li>Awesome Soundtrack<br></li><li>Great challenge to those with an adventurer's mindset</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867070/extras/d5cb92b0dc42d7f89f32f3a33022e115.avif?t=1643786199\" width=630 height=132 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867070/extras/a98aeb46f16c3747331b5279a2699715.avif?t=1643786199\" width=630 height=132 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867070/extras/9787412a5bb328a01332113a4dc051ee.avif?t=1643786199\" width=630 height=132 /></span>",
